## Context
Tracer bullet task. Implements the core error classification from spec 06. Depends on CliError/CliErrorCode types from src/types.ts (spawner-2oy) and adapter interface from src/adapters/types.ts (spawner-559) which defines classifyError per adapter.

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Shared PATTERNS array with regex patterns mapped to CliErrorCode, retryable flag, ordered by priority
- [ ] parseRetryAfterMs(text) extracts retry delay from stderr text, defaults to 60000
- [ ] classifyError(cli, exitCode, stderr, stdout) delegates to adapter's classifyError method
- [ ] Fallback: non-zero exit + no match → { code: 'fatal', retryable: false }
- [ ] Fallback: zero exit + no match → { code: 'unknown', retryable: false }
- [ ] CliError.message is concise (first matching line), raw is full stderr+stdout
- [ ] Export matchSharedPatterns() helper for adapters to reuse shared pattern table

## Files
- src/core/errors.ts (create) — parent dir created by spawner-cpx scaffold task

## Patterns
- See specs/06-error-classification.md for full pattern table and parseRetryAfterMs pseudocode
- See specs/planned/01-types-and-constants.md for CliError and CliErrorCode types
- Note: ENOENT/binary_not_found is handled at spawn level (spec 05), NOT in classifyError

## Tests
- rate_limit stderr → { code: 'rate_limit', retryable: true, retryAfterMs: 60000 }
- rate_limit with 'retry after 30 seconds' → retryAfterMs: 30000
- auth stderr → { code: 'auth', retryable: false }
- session_not_found stderr → { code: 'session_not_found', retryable: false }
- model_not_found stderr → { code: 'model_not_found', retryable: false }
- context_overflow stderr → { code: 'context_overflow', retryable: false }
- permission_denied stderr → { code: 'permission_denied', retryable: false }
- no match + non-zero exit → { code: 'fatal', retryable: false }
- no match + zero exit → { code: 'unknown', retryable: false }
- multiple patterns match → first in priority order wins
- raw field contains full stderr+stdout

## Verify
pnpm vitest run test/core/errors.test.ts
